name: NVJOB Image Filter Textual Inversion
description:
A small image filter.

  • Adds more realism.

  • Warm lighting.

  • Depth of field.

  • Correction of anatomy.

  • Natural colors.

Multiplier value: 0.3 - 2

NVJOB Image Filter Textual Inversion can be combined with NVJOB Image Filter Lora

nvjob.github.io/donate
